title: Umma's Lunch Box
typeOfFood: Buffet, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, Korean, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafeteria specializing in Korean food. Many of the buffet dishes seem vegan suitable - ask about use of fish and shrimp paste, etc. Has a small made-to-order menu. Sells reuseable containers that you could bring back for a discount. In 2014 changed its name from Le Chatel Bakery and Cafe.
